texts.text:
Mushrooms, a naturally-occurring non-solid block found in dark places with red and brown variants
Huge mushroom, a generated structure, a variant of small red and brown mushrooms
Mushroom Blocks, a solid block that comprises huge mushrooms
Mushroom Stem, a solid block that comprises huge mushrooms
Mushroom Stew, a food item crafted with mushrooms and a bowl
Mushroom Fields, a rare biome made up of mycelium and mushrooms
Mooshroom, a cow variant 'infected' with red or brown mushrooms
Brown Mooshroom, a brown variant of Mooshroom
Fungus, fungus that generates in the Nether
Huge fungus, a generated structure, a variant of crimson and warped fungus
Coral mushroom, a generated structure, made out of various coral blocks
Cluckshroom, a red mushroom variant of chicken

Mooshroom, an enemy in ???
Mooshroom Monstrosity, a boss variant of the Mooshroom
Fungus Thrower, an enemy in Flames of the Nether
Zombified Fungus Thrower, the zombified version of the Fungus Thrower
Death Cap Mushroom, an artifact
Blast Fungus, an artifact exclusive to the Flames of the Nether DLC
